Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types

Interface ImyhatConsumer

All Known Implementing Classes:
PackJsonArray, PackJsonObject, PackStreaming, PackWdlJsonArray, PackWdlJsonObject, PackWdlVariables, SHA1DigestSigner, ToBytesConverter
public interface ImyhatConsumer
Cpllect a value based on the provided information

In some cases, a Shesmu value may be passed to Java as Object and an accompanying Imyhat.
